{
  "description": "A serene evening scene depicts a sandy beach meeting calm waters with a backdrop of houses and a vibrant, dramatic sky. The sky is filled with layered, billowy clouds in shades of deep purple, gray, and hints of orange near the horizon, suggesting either a sunset or sunrise. A wooden boardwalk and several docked boats are visible on the left side of the frame, extending into the water. Along the beach, a concrete retaining wall runs parallel to the shoreline, supporting a row of houses. One house is prominently featured with multiple levels, balconies, and warm lighting emanating from within. A person stands with their back to the viewer, looking out towards the water, holding a bright orange object, likely a ball or toy. A paddleboard lies partially buried in the sand. The overall composition evokes a sense of tranquility and the beauty of coastal living.",
